-- Vestas Says Report Shows V112 Blade Accident Was ‘Human Error’
-- B y   C h r i s t i a n   W i e n b e r g
-- 2010-09-28T07:55:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/vestas-says-report-shows-v112-s-turbine-blade-accident-was-human-error-.html
 Vestas Wind Systems A/S said an
independent investigation concluded that “a human error”
caused the blade of its new V112-3.0 MW turbine to fall off.  The report by Det Norske Veritas “confirms Vestas’ own
conclusion,” the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christian Wienberg at 
 cwienberg@bloomberg.net  